fields.name: mask
fields.description: Parameters bitmask. Only the masked parameters will be applied. Bit definitions: bit 0: dynModel, bit 1: minEl, bit 2: posFixMode, bit 3: drLim, bit 4: posMask, bit 5: timeMask, bit 6: staticHoldMask, bit 7: dgpsMask, bit 8: cnoThreshold, bit 10: utc.

fields.name: dynModel
fields.description: Dynamic platform model: 0 = portable, 2 = stationary, 3 = pedestrian, 4 = automotive, 5 = sea, 6 = airborne with <1g acceleration, 7 = airborne with <2g acceleration, 8 = airborne with <4g acceleration, 9 = wrist-worn watch (not supported for protocol versions less than 18.00), 10 = bike (supported for protocol versions 19.20) (not supported for protocol versions less than 16.00)

fields.name: fixMode
fields.description: Position fixing mode: 1 = 2D only, 2 = 3D only, 3 = auto 2D/3D

fields.name: fixedAlt
fields.description: Fixed altitude (mean sea level) for 2D fix mode

fields.name: minElev
fields.description: Minimum elevation for a GNSS satellite to be used in NAV

fields.name: drLimit
fields.description: Reserved (maximum time to perform dead reckoning (linear extrapolation) in case of GPS signal loss, only applicable for protocol versions less than 14.00)

fields.name: dgnssTimeout
fields.description: DGNSS timeout (not supported for protocol versions less than 13.00)

fields.name: cnoThreshNumSVs
fields.description: Number of satellites required to have C/NO above cnoThresh for a fix to be attempted (not supported for protocol versions less than 14.00)

fields.name: cnoThresh
fields.description: C/NO threshold for deciding whether to attempt a fix (not supported for protocol versions less than 14.00)

fields.name: staticHoldMaxDist
fields.description: Static hold distance threshold (before quitting static hold) (not supported for protocol versions less than 15.00)
